Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,清爽秋风吹走夏日倦怠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,潇洒推理秀出青春本色
